Package: longitudinalPCoA
Title: Adjusted PCoA Plots for Longitudinal and Hierarchical Microbiome Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Amarise", "Little", , "amarise@fredhutch.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:  This package provides functions to perform PCA analysis on longitudinal and hierarchical microbiome data using a kernel matrix, with adjustment for confounding variables and repeated measures via linear mixed models.
